        <h3>TRAVELING ENGAGEMENT CENTER</h3>
        <p>The ABS Engagement Center has the unique ability to attract the  attention of young people, helping them identify with the need for  Scripture and become involved with furthering the work of making  Scripture available for all people.</p>
