        <p>You will spend the majority of your time in the Engagement Center.  Thanks to your time and energy, all will experience the life changing  message of the Bible! You&prime;ll help ABS in its efforts to:</p>
        <p>Emphasize the importance of Bible Engagement 4+ (four or more) times  a week and excite the audience with new and innovative Scripture  resources made possible by American Bible Society.</p>
        <p>Join local church efforts to get congregants &quot;back to the basics&quot; by  calling members to a new or renewed practice of daily Scripture.</p>
